wikipedia_page.main: William Rudolph Michael Feilding, 11th Earl of Denbigh, 10th Earl of Desmond (2 August 1943 – 23 March 1995), was a British peer. He married Caroline Judith Vivienne Cooke on 2 September 1965. They had three children: Lady Samantha, Lady Louisa, and Alexander, the current 12th Earl of Denbigh and 11th Earl of Desmond. He was an advertising executive, pop group promoter, and Rolls-Royce dealer.

response: Alexander Stephen Rudolph Feilding, 12th Earl of Denbigh, 11th Earl of Desmond (born 4 November 1970), styled Viscount Feilding until 1995, is a member of the British aristocracy and son of William Feilding, 11th Earl of Denbigh and his wife Judy née Cooke.
